{
  "texts": [
    "These vessels-by-features tables were used in scanpy to cluster the vessels in each sample to remove regions incorrectly identified as portal or central vessels, such as some tissue margins.",
    "Lastly, to home in on the vessel proper, we used the nuclei segmentation mask (see next section) and scikit-image to find areas without nuclei.",
    "These regions were intersected with the vessel areas identified previously to obtain the focused vessel region.",
    "4i data-nuclei-centered analysis.",
    "Nuclei masks for each sample were produced using cellpose 58 based on the DAPI channel from the first elution cycle."
  ]
}